\begin_inset Formula $e$
\end_inset

 variable into the 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "AT TESS microdata"
target "https://github.com/huntallcott/BehavioralPublicProblemSet/blob/master/analysis/input/PreppedTESSData.dta"
literal "false"

\end_inset

